#: data/campaigns/Liberty/scenarios/03_A_Strategy_Of_Hope.cfg:129
#, fuzzy
msgid "Defeat both enemy leaders"
msgstr "Sconfiggi il generale nemico"

#: data/campaigns/Liberty/scenarios/03_A_Strategy_Of_Hope.cfg:141
#, fuzzy
